   - USB-Disk up to 32GB (FAT16, FAT32)
   - supports mp3 sampling rate 8KHz, 11.025KHz, 12KHz, 16KHz, 22.05KHz, 24KHz, 32KHz, 44.1KHz, 48KHz
   - supports up to 100 folders, each folder can be assigned to 001..255 songs
